(secondQuint)Impact of Labour Kinesiotherapy in the Quality Life of Auxiliary Nursing in the Surgery Center.

 The activities in the work routine can cause pain and negatively affect quality of life.

 There is the hypothesis that gymnastics may be used for pain and injuries relating to repetitive movement at work.

 Objective the study is assess the impact of labor kinesiotherapy in the quality of life of the operating room nursing assistants.

